Package: j0j0r
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the j0j0 terms in the CTS model of Bindslev 1996
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Morten Stejner
Maintainer: Morten Stejner <mstejner@gmail.com>
Description: Package to calculate terms in the  unscreened current fluctuation 
    correlation tensor in the CTS model of Bindslev 1996, JATP 58, 983. 
    Can in princple handle arbitrary velocity distributions, and users are free 
    to define new distributions. 
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
